      <P>This page enables you to restart the system, save and load different
settings as profiles, restore factory default settings, run a <A HREF="#tools_setup_wizard">setup
wizard</A> to configure router settings, upgrade the <A HREF="glossary.asp#def_firmware">firmware</A>,
and <A HREF="glossary.asp#def_Ping">ping</A> remote IP addresses.</P>
      <P> Click the items below for more information:</P>
      <UL>
        <LI CLASS="mvd-P-Bullet">
